<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1273456-this-is-an-amazing-book-detailing-the">This is an amazing book detailing the proliferation of the American nuclear arsenal with all of its issues and near-misses. Does anyone know of a similar book that deals with Soviet proliferation and near misses? Specifically detailing the Stanislav Petrov incident and others.</a>
</div>
