<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/33671976-david-tussey"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1436813929i/33671976._UY100_CR9,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/33671976-david-tussey">David Tussey</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">&quot;The Bomb&quot; by Fred Kaplan. Similar in that it reviews US (and Soviet) nuclear war policy and practices. Excellent read.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">"The Bomb" by Fred Kaplan. Similar in that it reviews US (and Soviet) nuclear war policy and practices. Excellent read.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
