<span id="freeTextContainer10729088723236456322">A fantastic and frightening account of our nuclear armament situation. The fact we haven&apos;t blown up the world accidentally is shocking and Schlosser shows exactly how close we have come (many times over). A required read for anyone interested in the Cold War or systematic failures of the government. </span>
  <span id="freeText10729088723236456322" style="display:none">A fantastic and frightening account of our nuclear armament situation. The fact we haven't blown up the world accidentally is shocking and Schlosser shows exactly how close we have come (many times over). A required read for anyone interested in the Cold War or systematic failures of the government. </span>
